"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931774-Olympics-2024-Donna-Vekic-nightmare-silver-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Donna Vekic revealed that she almost skipped the Paris 2024 Games before becoming the first Croatian woman ever to win a medal in the tennis event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999518918241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Donna Vekic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donna_Veki\\u0107\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8726922624386989, \"rank\": 0.05690573042017964, \"text\": \"Croatian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old had a nightmare start to her Olympics journey when she got sick and her flight was cancelled.\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But a few days later, she walked away with the silver medal.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a standout summer for Vekic, who reached the final in Bad Homburg and got to her first Grand Slam semi-final atWimbledon.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.999911379945179, \"rank\": 8.862790910781163e-05, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after her heroics at SW19, she almost gave up on the Olympics.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After Wimbledon semi-finals I had so much pain everywhere that I was debating going to the Olympics because I thought, okay, in these conditions there is no way I can win a medal,\\\" the world No.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"21 said afterlosing to Qinwen Zheng in the gold medal match.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999999938609, \"rank\": 6.1536277011167784e-12, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had pain in my arm, pain in my ankle, I was sick.\\\"\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that wasn't the only barrier Vekic faced in her journey to the silver medal.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Everything was happening all at once.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When we came here, first our flight was cancelled, we arrived late.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything was going wrong.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When we had our first practice, I told my coach, I was coughing so bad I could not hit two shots in a row.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Roger Federer makes feelings on Andy Murray clear after Olympics retirement  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \